{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so in our parties, and then we went for walks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was always organized that an accidental meeting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, we're going to meet me here and there, but accidentally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And usually if you were with somebody else and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we separated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, tried to make it as-- as natural as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because one-- that place was full of left behind-- not only German agents, but then we-- we discovered Arab-- Arab-- Arab spies who were spying for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After all, the Germans were pretty close and left the-- the bastard behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, well, we--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- then-- then we came to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's-- that's in my book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That then we to-- we went to the-- to theatres.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or we went to-- went to resorts there, where the officers resort, of swimming pool and so on, and this kind-- we took-- took a long walk from that-- from that resort there, walking back to the-- back to the center.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the time where, then, where we really stopped, looked at each other, embraced, and well, my [INAUDIBLE], we were made to each other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But took quite a while.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we did say--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just-- just in a [INAUDIBLE] as we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were just the-- I mean, the-- the hell and whole assignment and our mission was ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when you are in that-- in that service, you never, never think about dying or anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have your full confidence that am I going to pull through, go through with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the subconscious-- in the subconscious there is that, I never can-- never return from this kind of of hell.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but-- but-- but then-- then we planned.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
